# Web3Forms access key — bound to the destination email at signup.
# Get one free at https://web3forms.com/ using hello@cicanda.com.
# The NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix is required because Web3Forms' free tier only accepts
# client-side submissions; the key is designed to be public per their docs.
# Copy this file to .env.local and paste the key below.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
